<p>So yeah, not doing great. I&#8217;m not sure if I can blame that on my ignorance of AMC or if I should just wait out the call. The stock dropped over 40% last week and has mostly rebounded since &#8211; but that&#8217;s 10 days of huge volatility and I&#8217;ve been hearing good things about the day trade there regardless of what the fundamentals are. <a href="http://davosbtc.wordpress.com/2013/07/09/amc-and-self-scoring-analyst-calls/" rel="bookmark">&#8734;</a></p>
