	<h2><a href="http://davosbtc.wordpress.com/2013/06/27/security-blog-moves/" rel="bookmark">Securities Blog Moves, Analysis Blog Begins; or, &#8220;Meet the New Blog, Same as the Old&nbsp;Blog&#8221;</a></h2>
	<p class="entry-meta">
		<a href="http://davosbtc.wordpress.com/2013/06/27/security-blog-moves/" title="Permanent Link to Securities Blog Moves, Analysis Blog Begins; or, &#8220;Meet the New Blog, Same as the Old&nbsp;Blog&#8221;" rel="bookmark">June 27, 2013 3:47 pm</a> / <a href="http://davosbtc.wordpress.com/2013/06/27/security-blog-moves/#respond" title="Comment on Securities Blog Moves, Analysis Blog Begins; or, &#8220;Meet the New Blog, Same as the Old&nbsp;Blog&#8221;">Leave a comment</a>	</p><!-- end .entry-meta -->
	<div class="entry-summary"><p>I&#8217;ve decided to move my irregular Crypto-Securities &#8216;index&#8217; reports to a dedicated blog and begin using this blog for (hopefully) more regular commentary and deeper analysis of crypto-securities. I&#8217;ve already done the latest two updates on securities rankings (now available at <a title="BTCindex" href="http://btcindex.wordpress.com/2013/06/21/6_21_2013_top_crypto_securities_report/">BTCindex</a>). I&#8217;ll also be using this blog to contribute my thoughts to ongoing discussion topics across the bitcoin sphere.</p>
</div>

